      <title>印度一年来最大规模 IPO 后，Bharti Hexacom 股价上涨 50%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/bharti-hexacom-set-to-debut-after-india-s-biggest-ipo-in-a-year</link>
